    data crossing 4 categorical variables, none are hierarchical.

    Source: R/data.R
    datatest1.Rd

    data crossing 4 categorical variables, none are hierarchical.

    Usage

    datatest1

    Format

    A tibble/data frame with 689 rows and 12 variables:

    A10

    business sector, not hierarchical

    cj

    legal category, not hierarchical

    type_distrib

    type of distribution, not hierarchical

    treff

    Number of employees (categorical), not hierarchical

    nb_obs

    Frequency, number of companies

    nb_obs_rnd

    Frequency rounded, number of companies

    pizzas_tot

    turnover value in euros

    pizzas_tot_abs

    turnover absolute value in euros

    pizzas_max

    turnover max value in euros

    is_secret_freq

    Boolean, TRUE if primary secret for frequency rule

    is_secret_dom

    Boolean, TRUE if primary secret for dominance rule

    is_secret_prim

    Boolean, TRUE if primary secret for any rule
